{"tid":1550202,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"克警想捉孖生姊妹返狗屋玩姊妹丼!!!","createTime":"2019-09-07T14:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T17:48:07.000Z","uid":90577,"like":22,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"579d26bcde28661afb4b77ce92abaf3e52835003","tid":1550202,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:57:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cuspcusp/photos/a.764090536985026/2477976375596425/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcuspcusp%2Fphotos%2Fa.764090536985026%2F2477976375596425%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQCwmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=e2c6e012\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cuspcusp/photos/a.764090536985026/2477976375596425/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n王先生一家四口在旺角警署門外等交通燈過馬路。誰知速龍小隊喝罵他們過馬路，他們堅持等待至綠燈才過。警員立刻包圍孖生姊妹，卻放行其父母，還對姊妹說：「拉咗佢哋兩個番上去先講。後生似示威者」。及後王媽媽對警員説普通話才沒事。<br />\n<br />\n王先生及其妻子過後猶有餘悸，王媽媽更激動得失聲痛哭，表示：「白色恐怖，人間地獄。」<br />\n<br />\nPOPO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBTW,對孖生姊妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd482edbb062b881596fd8ac14a1909f67c8af9d","tid":1550202,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:57:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><